===Etymology===
Attested since the mid 16th century, of uncertain origin. Suggestions include connection with Irish Gaelic {{m|ga|cauch||cup}} (whence Scots {{m|sco|quaich}}, {{m|sco|queff}}). The noun is derived from the verb, since the later 16th century.

